item.title: CVE-2022-4109|2024-08-03T01:27:54.413Z -- unknown -- wholesale%20market%20for%20woocommerce
item.description: The Wholesale Market for WooCommerce WordPress plugin before 2.0.0 does not validate user input against path traversal attacks, allowing high privilege users such as admin to download arbitrary logs from the server even when they should not be able to (for example in multisite)

item.title: CVE-2022-4106|2024-08-03T01:27:54.544Z -- unknown -- wholesale%20market%20for%20woocommerce
item.description: The Wholesale Market for WooCommerce WordPress plugin before 1.0.7 does not have authorisation check, as well as does not validate user input used to generate system path, allowing unauthenticated attackers to download arbitrary file from the server.
